{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ace236a3f6","title":"复曾泽生等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1ef78641ed","index":0,"year":1948,"month":10,"day":27,"articleId":"ace236a3f6"}],"tags":[{"id":"a7ea3bd8ce","name":"朱德","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji25","name":"毛泽东全集第25卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji25.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji25":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f0bf8d8b60","type":"paragraph","text":"复曾泽生等电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"ace236a3f6"},{"id":"935b47f9fd","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年10月27日）曾军长、白师长、刘师长，并转全军官兵均鉴十月十七日电蒸。贵军在长春举义，加入人民解放军，便长春获得有秩序的解放，深塘欣感。贵军长等此次行动，应当为东北与全国一切愿意觉悟的国民党军队官兵所效法。希望贵军长等在林司令员、罗政委直接领导之下，团结全军，力求进步，改善官兵与军民关系，与全国人民解放军并肩作战，为盟逐美日侵略势力，打值国民党反动派，建立新中国而奋斗","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"ace236a3f6"},{"id":"21955a7ca6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东朱德","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"ace236a3f6"},{"id":"ea09c55e3e","type":"paragraph","text":"十月二十七日[1]这是毛泽东和朱德给在长春率部起义的国民党军六十军军长警泽生","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"ace236a3f6"}],"page":{"id":"7c7261b203","publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"ace236a3f6","start":125,"end":125}}}},"__N_SSG":true}